{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "tiphub-public-data-api-v1",
    "name": "Tiphub Public Data API",
    "description": "# Tiphub Public Data API\n\nA curated collection of Tiphub data endpoints for accessing Indian stock market data.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. Set  to  (default)\n2. Set  — get one from the [Tiphub Developer Portal](https://tiphub.ai/developer)\n3. All endpoints use the  header for authentication\n\n## Rate Limits\n\n| Tier | Requests/min |\n|------|--------------|\n| Basic | 30 |\n| Premium | 120 |\n\n## Data Coverage\n\n- **Exchange:** NSE (National Stock Exchange of India)\n- **Stocks:** 3,000+ tickers\n- **Timeframes:** 1-minute to monthly OHLC\n- **Fundamentals:** Market cap, PE ratios, margins, dividends, and more\n- **News:** Financial news via Google News",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://tiphub.ai",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_ticker",
      "value": "RELIANCE",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_task_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
